Privacy Policy LS Garage
Effective Date: May 31, 2024
This Privacy Policy applies to the game
LS Garage
by Gleb Bibikov (Bibikov Games), which we here call the Service. If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this Privacy Policy. We may periodically update this Privacy Policy by posting a new version on lsgarage.ru/privacy. Your continued use of the Service after the effective date will be subject to the new Privacy Policy.
This Privacy Policy describes what personal data we collect and how we use your personal data.
What data do we collect
Data you provide us directly:
- player name (or you can use random player name);
- other data you choose to give us (such as email or data to identify a lost account).
Data we collect automatically:
- data about your account and game progress;
- data about your use of the Service, such as gameplay data and your interactions with other players inside the Service;
- your IP address;
- data about your device and operating system;
- data we collect with cookies and similar technologies (see more below);
- analytics and crash data.
Data we collect from our partners:
We also use third-party partners, such as social networking sites, data analytics providers to supplement information we have about you, such as:
- data we receive if you link a third party tool with the Service (such as Google or Facebook);
- data from platforms that the games run on (such as Google Play or App Store to verify payment);
- data for analytics purposes.
Why do we collect your data
We process data necessary to:
- create accounts and allow you to play our game and use our Service;
- operate the Service;
- verify and confirm payments;
- provide and deliver services you request.
To provide a great Service to our players, we collect and process necessary data to:
- develop and improve the Service and player experience;
- manage our relationship with you;
- customize your Service experience;
- provide the best gaming experience possible.
In order to keep the Service features safe and fair, to fight fraud, we process necessary data to:
- analyze and monitor use of the Service;
- take action against fraudulent or misbehaving players.
In all of the above cases and purposes, we may analyze, profile and segment all collected data.
Who can see and use your data
Apart from Gleb Bibikov (Bibikov Games), your data can be accessed by others in the certain situations.
Other players and users:
Social features are a core component of our game. Other players and users may, for example, see your profile data and in-game activities. Users are encouraged not to create a player name that reflects their own name or other personal information.
Our service providers:
We have vendors to us provide the Services. These vendors process your data only at and according to instructions to provide the Service, and perform tasks such as hosting, player support, advertising, analytics and fraud prevention.
Partners:
The Service includes features from our partners, such as social media interaction tools, functionalities through application programming interfaces (APIs) or software development kits (SDKs). These partners may access your data and operate under their own privacy policies. We encourage you to check their privacy policies to learn more about their data processing practices.
These partners may access data regarding your activities and your device (such as your IP address, mobile identifiers, location).
