Other companies and public authorities:
In order to combat fraud and illegal activity, we may process and disclose data with other companies and organizations and provide it to public authorities in response to lawful requests.
We may also disclose your data based on your consent, to comply with the law or to protect the rights, property or safety of us, our players or others.
Cookies and similar technologies
Like most online services, we and our partners use cookies and similar technologies to provide and personalize the Service, analyse use and prevent fraud. Cookies are files with a small amount of data commonly used as anonymous unique identifiers. Cookies and similar technologies allow us and our partners to store their preferences and track your activities within the Service. We and our partners collect and store information about users' interactions with application that use our technologies, including cookies and similar tracking technologies.
We do so for:
- analytics and personalization;
- detecting and preventing fraud.
Application permissions
Service may request certain types of in-game permissions. We may require these permissions for the following reasons:
- photos/media/files for storing game data on the device;
- in-app purchases to enable in-app purchases.
Children
Our Service are not directed to children under 13 (or other age as required by local law). We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13.
If we become aware that a child has provided us with personal data, we will delete any personal data we have collected, unless we have a legal obligation to keep it, and terminate the child’s account and/or revert them to the underage experience, as applicable.
Users under the age of 18 are not allowed to use paid services without the permission of the parents or legal guardians.
Age restrictions may vary depending on the country in which the user resides.
How do we protect your data
In order to help ensure a secure and safe player experience, we are continuously developing and implementing administrative, technical and physical security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or against loss, misuse or alteration. No method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure, however.  We cannot assume responsibility or liability for unauthorized access to our servers and systems.
Data retention
We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you the Service. We may for example periodically de-identify unused game accounts, and we may regularly review and de-identify unnecessary data.
Your rights and options
If you request, we will provide you a copy of your personal data in an electronic format.
You also have the right to correct your data, have your data deleted, object how we use or share your data, and restrict how we use or share your data. We will respond to all requests within a reasonable timeframe.
If you wish to exercise any of your data subject rights, please use the support options described in "Contact Us". We will respond to all requests in accordance with applicable laws. To protect your privacy, we may also take additional steps to verify your identity before fulfilling your request, such as by requesting you provide us a purchase receipt or other account information, or asking you to answer questions regarding your activities on our Service.
Contact us
If you have questions about data protection, or if you have any requests for resolving issues with your personal data, we encourage you to primarily contact us by email:
contact@lsgarage.ru